<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，你听说了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="33" />的第一个活动<delay8 />
很快就要开始啦！
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />究竟会是怎样的活动呢，<delay20 />
光是想一想就感觉好兴奋～！<delay40 />
到时候<delay8 /><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定要尽全力去享受才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这一天终于要来了，<delay20 />
明天就是<tag a="110" b="33" />上<delay8 />
第一个活动的日子啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这是对整个<tag a="110" b="32" />来说特别重要的一天，<delay20 />
大家可要热热闹闹的，<delay8 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />开一个好头才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下个周六就是钓鱼大赛哦～<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />要参加的话，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我也不能轻易认输呀～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在比赛开始前，<delay20 />我得好好挑一下<delay8 />
要穿去比赛的衣服才行！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是钓鱼大赛啦～<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果能钓上大鱼来，<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />一定会非常激动吧！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过要是养在家里的话，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我还是更喜欢小一点的鱼，<delay20 />
因为比较可爱呀～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />下个周六是捕虫大赛哦～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过你看啊，<delay8 />小心翼翼地接近虫子
然后把它抓住，<delay20 />
是会让人很紧张对吧？<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且我又是说话停不住的类型，<delay20 />
要我静～悄悄地，偷～偷摸摸地靠近它们，<delay8 />
是有那么一点难呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天就是捕虫大赛啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我才刚买了新的捕虫网，<delay8 />
真想赶快用用看啊～！<pageBreak /><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最后究竟能抓到多少只呢？<delay20 />
我现在就好心急，都憋不住啦～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />对了对了，<delay8 /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay40 />
<anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明天快乐家协会那边<delay8 />
会把打分结果发回来哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我对这一次的<delay20 />家装搭配<delay8 />
可是超～级有信心的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过呢，<delay8 />担心还是有的～<delay20 />
就是怕<delay8 />负责评分的人无法理解我的品位<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这么一点小事吧～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="018" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我说我说，<delay20 /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay8 />
你看过快乐家协会<delay8 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />发回来的打分结果了吗～？
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我、<delay8 />我还没看呢～<delay40 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等到舞蹈课结束之后
就能看到啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="019" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />再过不久，<delay8 />今年也就结束啦～<delay40 />
真期待迎新年的时刻呀！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />31日我们会在广场上一起倒计时，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大家一起来玩个痛快吧！<delay40 />
<anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />到时候可得通宵哦～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="90" b="27" />年也要在明天结束啦～<delay40 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />总感觉这一年好像只在一瞬间，<delay20 />
又好像过了好久好久呀！
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最后这一天，<delay20 />
大家一起来一场盛大的倒计时，<delay20 />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />迎来欢乐的新年吧～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>